metadata.name: The corporate journalism
metadata.description:
Every day the maSter speaks.  
What does he is really want from us ?  
What is the hidden desire inside his unconscious mind ? 

The $ubject is an artistic experience combining data streams and AI. It analyzes the words of a maSter and transforms them into visual representations of his unconscious.

Data stream => AI => Artwork

attributes.value: Why is corporate journalism rushing to defend the state instead of the people?
